# Backup

## 8. Backup de Secrets

```bash
for secret in $(az keyvault secret list \
  --vault-name "$SOURCE_VAULT" \
  --query "[].name" -o tsv); do

  echo "Backup secret: $secret"

  az keyvault secret backup \
    --vault-name "$SOURCE_VAULT" \
    --name "$secret" \
    --file "$BACKUP_DIR/secrets/$secret.bak"
done
```

---

